    "body": "One problem with the hashing method as described above: you would have to parse the filled test JSON to find out what hash to look at. Parsing JSON is relatively slow.\r\n\r\nInstead, could store a separate file with a list of `filledFileName: fillerHash`. Would be quicker to cycle through, and clients wouldn't have to change testing infrastructure to deal with new `fillerHash` field in filled tests.",
